{"tid":604661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"糗！中國CBA頒MVP獎項 獎盃竟和淘寶水果盤同款...","createTime":"2018-03-25T02:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T05:34:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8c74d0ff421fc32e024dc331b9237a266c613aee","tid":604661,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php0Qxwoq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php0Qxwoq.jpg&h=ace7832d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕糗！中國男子籃球職業聯賽（CBA）日前頒發本季最有價值球員（MVP）獎項，由山東隊球員丁彥雨航當選，他獲獎時開心捧著鮮花和獎盃，不料有眼尖的網友發現，MVP獎盃竟和淘寶賣的水果盤一模一樣，且折合台幣才600元。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，CBA獎盃被發現和淘寶賣的水果盤激似，引起中國網友討論，有人開玩笑問，「買了水果盤就能成為最有價值球員嗎？」淘寶的賣家則表示，的確是同一款，但沒有附底座，有人因而發問，「不附底座的話，膠水有嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n其他網友開玩笑留言，認為堂堂一個CBA聯賽竟然顯得這麼廉價，也有人翻出資料照，幾年前的頒獎儀式也曾發生MVP獎盃當場分屍，當年就已發現獎座是用膠水黏的，另外有網友直說，「淘寶和MVP的距離只差一個底座。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpMVkGC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpMVkGC1.jpg&h=3718e5f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2375840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2375840&d=vYDgsfdcTD8A37J%2B7TckUb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=84fbbeec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2375840&h=f22d0cb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2375840</a>"},{"pid":"ff65c09aff6b1ad09c9cbd8e3cd073c401f4602d","tid":604661,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"留名等睇告抄襲"},{"pid":"c8cb183342b0a053023e33e013ad0672fcb45aee","tid":604661,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT